item.title: Mister Rogers Remixed | Garden of Your Mind | PBS Digital Studios
item.description:
Mister Rogers Remixed | Garden of Your Mind | PBS Digital Studios
Mister Rogers remixed by Symphony of Science's John Boswell for PBS Digital Studios. **If you like this video, please support your local PBS station.** http://www.pbs.org/donate (Headphones highly recommended!) When we discovered video mash-up artist John D. Boswell, aka melodysheep, on YouTube, we immediately wanted to work together. Turns out that he is a huge Mister Rogers Neighborhood fan, and was thrilled at the chance to pay tribute to one of our heroes. Both PBS and the Fred Rogers Company hope you like John's celebration of Fred Rogers' message. This is the first in a series of PBS icons remixed. Many thanks to the folks at the Fred Rogers Company for their support. More from melodysheep: http://www.youtube.com/melodysheep Subscribe to PBS Digital Studios: http://www.youtube.com/pbsdigitalstudios On Twitter: @pbsds
